Serialized Form

  • Package DataItems

    • Class DataItems.Link extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • from

          String from
          IDs of connected nodes. from = start, to = destination.

        • to

          String to
          IDs of connected nodes. from = start, to = destination.

    • Class DataItems.Node extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • ID

          String ID
          ID of the node. This will be the filename of the page upon creation, and is used for linking.

        • imagePath

          String imagePath
          The path to the image to display on this page.

        • links

          com.google.common.collect.Multimap<String,​String> links
          Multimap to hold links to other nodes.

          Key is the ID, value is the hyperlink text.

        • paragraph

          String paragraph
          Paragraph of the node. Put the main "meat" of the page's text here.

        • title

          String title
          Title of the node. Shown at the top of the screen in the finished page.

    • Class DataItems.NodeRectangle extends Rectangle implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • node

          Node node
          The node that this rectangle represents.

        • upperLeft

          Point upperLeft
          The upper-left corner of the rectangle.

    • Class DataItems.PageEditorData extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • ID

          String ID
          Fields for the title, ID, and paragraph of the node.

        • linkPanels

          ArrayList<LinkPanel> linkPanels
          Record of the panels added, so the last one may be removed with the user presses the '-' button in the editor.

        • otherNodes

          ArrayList<NodeRectangle> otherNodes
          List of other nodes that can be connected to from this node Should be just about any node in the project file.

          Links from a node to itself are allowed.

        • paragraph

          String paragraph
          Fields for the title, ID, and paragraph of the node.

        • title

          String title
          Fields for the title, ID, and paragraph of the node.

    • Class DataItems.ProjectFile extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • authorName

          String authorName
          Author of the project.

        • nodes

          ArrayList<NodeRectangle> nodes
          The main meat of the tool. An ArrayList of all of the nodes/pages in the current file.

        • projectTitle

          String projectTitle
          Title of the project.

        • visualLinks

          ArrayList<Link> visualLinks
          An ArrayList of links between the nodes in the file. This is mainly for the View to use.
